    "href": "assignments/assignment-1.html#creating-a-new-dataset-and-replacing-missing-values",
    "title": "Assignment 1",
    "section": "Creating a New Dataset and Replacing Missing Values",
    "text": "Creating a New Dataset and Replacing Missing Values\n\nnew_data &lt;- df\n\nfor (col in names(new_data)) {\n  if (is.factor(new_data[[col]])) {\n    new_data[[col]] &lt;- as.character(new_data[[col]])\n  }\n  if (is.numeric(new_data[[col]])) {\n    new_data[[col]][is.na(new_data[[col]])] &lt;- my_birth_year + k\n  } else if (is.character(new_data[[col]])) {\n    new_data[[col]][is.na(new_data[[col]])] &lt;- paste0(my_first, \"_\", k)\n  }\n}",
    "crumbs": [
